1. *Tužno* je što se sve ovo dogodilo. (It's sad that all this happened.)
2. U njegovim očima mogao se videti *tužan* pogled. (In his eyes there was a sad look.)
3. *Tužnim* glasom je rekao da je bolesna. (He said in a sad voice that she was sick.)
4. *Tužno* je kada nemaš nikoga da ti pruži podršku. (It's sad when you don't have anyone to give you support.)
5. *Tužnoj* devojci je potrebno mnogo ljubavi. (The sad girl needs a lot of love.)